{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_017EocGyxhBqtBiXLVadGDfp","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_0134jjdPegciWBQQp5KNGGW4","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Roasted Beet and Goat Cheese Salad.generated.18.txt","content":"Roasted Beet and Goat Cheese Salad\n\nThis vibrant salad celebrates the earthy sweetness of roasted beets paired with tangy goat cheese.\nA classic combination found in French bistros, it's surprisingly simple to prepare at home. The beets\ncan be roasted ahead of time, making this an excellent choice for entertaining. The warm beets work\nbeautifully with cool, creamy goat cheese while a bright vinaigrette brings everything together.\nServe this at room temperature for the most elegant presentation, or slightly warm for a cozy dinner.\n\nIngredients (serves 4)\n\n1.5 lbs fresh beets (red and golden mix if possible)\n4 oz goat cheese, crumbled\n6 cups mixed greens (arugula, spinach, frisée)\n1/4 cup toasted walnuts, chopped\n1/4 cup red onion, thinly sliced\n2 tbsp balsamic vinegar\n3 tbsp extra-virgin olive oil\n1 tbsp Dijon mustard\n1 tsp honey\n2 cloves garlic, minced\nSalt and freshly ground pepper\nFresh dill for garnish\n\nInstructions\n\n1. Preheat oven to 400°F. Wash beets and wrap individually in foil\n2. Roast for 45-50 minutes until fork-tender\n3. Cool slightly, then peel away skin under running water\n4. Cut beets into wedges and set aside\n5. Whisk together vinegar, mustard, honey, and garlic\n6. Slowly whisk in olive oil until emulsified\n7. Season dressing with salt and pepper\n8. Toss greens with half the dressing\n9. Arrange greens on plates, top with warm beets\n10. Scatter goat cheese, walnuts, and red onion\n11. Drizzle remaining dressing and fresh dill\n12. Serve immediately\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":566,"cache_read_input_tokens":81183,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":566},"output_tokens":6,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b9a7c1af-9751-4310-853d-8c46d3069c79","uuid":"829c6872-d5c8-4433-a592-bf84182148e2"}
